item.title: The Pedo Ring Series Summary of Episodes
item.description: 'Excellent stories, I've loved every one of the series so far. The best part is the realism of them; I really don't like stories with little girls who LOVE being gang-raped and so on. Hannah would obviously rather not have to do the things she does, which comes across beautifully in your writing.' - Review.
